{"tid":2450013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭博：南華早報恐面臨中央控制 本港媒體自由或再受重挫","createTime":"2021-03-17T05:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T06:25:57.000Z","uid":39464,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9e4420f6a709649ac854277b83bfb550ef8432","tid":2450013,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》早前報道關於內地政府要求阿里巴巴（9988）出售部分媒體資產，當中包括《南華早報》。《彭博社》引述《南華早報》員工指，擔心中國國有企業最終可能接手《南華早報》，並將該報置於北京的控制之下。報道形容，此舉將是香港媒體行業遭受的最重大打擊之一。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述香港大學新聞及傳媒研究中心總監兼香港外國記者會主席瑞凱德(Keith Richburg)指，「在北京那邊談論媒體必須由『愛國者』營運時傳出《南華早報》可能出售的消息，非常、非常令人擔憂。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1615957285743&amp;issue=20210317\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1615957285743%26issue%3D20210317&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=78324d8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1615957285743&amp;issue=20210317</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-16/jack-ma-s-scmp-joins-hong-kong-media-groups-facing-china-control\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021-03-16%2Fjack-ma-s-scmp-joins-hong-kong-media-groups-facing-china-control&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=8ac2a77c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2021-03-16/jack-ma-s-scmp-joins-hong-kong-media-groups-facing-china-control</a>"},{"pid":"57badce2cab9f1cb19add48ec40ef54e0afae4d1","tid":2450013,"uid":53105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:47:12.000Z","msg":"吓..."},{"pid":"957fde4bf077df5f608e05d506466e4d5ff39971","tid":2450013,"uid":550,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T05:51:04.000Z","msg":"南早曾幾何時係全世界最好賺嘅報館<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4146c7cdf7a638f02574a6d5